column5: AIRI Should be a private company All week Im trying to buy 2k lousy shares to round out my position 2k total shares trading today on a huge market day Board should just take private at 350 all cash to shareholders NOT A PUBLIC COMPANY

AIRI i was hoping wed make a push back to 110s today but onto next week closing the laptop up and going to try to enjoy some time on the lake before thunderstorms get here this weekend Everyone enjoy their weekend and i appreciate all you guys who share your DD here on this board
